{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"32e3a756a1","title":"致彭德怀、张宗逊、赵寿山电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c5f95df65e","index":0,"year":1949,"month":7,"day":19,"articleId":"32e3a756a1"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"1209eec314","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"32e3a756a1","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的致彭德怀、张宗逊、赵寿山电的主要内容。"},{"id":"c60fd3e1e0","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"32e3a756a1","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"第一野战军向中共中央军委报告，为追开青海的马步芳部和宁夏的马鸿透部，准备以第一、第二兵团出陇县，截击陇东；估计两马将总撤退，准备以第十九兵团沿西兰公路猛追。"},{"id":"3a07244bb3","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"32e3a756a1","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"发城，旧县名，今分属勉县和汉中市。"},{"id":"11db0e4f8c","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"32e3a756a1","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"南山，指秦岭山脉以南的汉中、勉县、南郑地区。"}],"contents":[{"id":"e612ded83a","type":"title","text":"致彭德怀、张宗逊、赵寿山电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"32e3a756a1"},{"id":"1209eec314","type":"paragraph","text":"以三个兵团追歼两马是否足够。我们觉得似应从十八兵团抽四至五个师西进，作为预备队。如这样做，便须该兵团集中主力攻占凤县、留坝，威肠袋城可（但可不占裹城），追使南山可敌军后撤，然后该兵团可以抽出四至五个师西进助战。是否应当如此，请","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"32e3a756a1"},{"id":"c60fd3e1e0","type":"subtitle","text":"酪办。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"32e3a756a1"}],"page":{"id":"8a23cb8759","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"32e3a756a1","start":63,"end":63}}}},"__N_SSG":true}